Package: RStudioStataConsole
Type: Package
Title: RStudio addin that facilitates running Stata in RStudio's termial.
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Sebastian Kranz
Maintainer: Sebastian Kranz <sebastian.kranz@uni-ulm.de>
Description: If you like to use Stata interactively on a web server (or in a docker container),
  you could access the Stata console version using a Terminal in an RStudio Server session in
  the browser. This small packages has three short addins that simplify this process.
  It is assumed that the Stata is installed and the `stata` command is on the path.
License: GPL >= 3.0
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Depends: rstudioapi, haven
